{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make teaching BSL mandatory in all schools",
        "additional_details": "I think it\u2019s disgusting that in 2024 BSL is not mandatory in schools.  When deaf children start school I want them to be able to communicate with other kids and thrive in a normal school environment, but until there\u2019s a change it won't be possible. I believe it's about time it\u2019s added to the curriculum!",
        "background": "There are about 50,000 deaf children in the UK. I would like the Government to make all schools introduce British sign language as a mandatory lesson in the curriculum.",
